name: Cargolux Boeing 747-8F [LX-VCF] Snowy Landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
A rare daylight arrival! I was pretty happy to see this coming in at a reasonable time ;) 
Here we have a Cargolux Airlines International Boeing 747-8R7F landing at Calgary International Airport, arriving from Seattle. Unfortunately I wasn't able to catch the departure, but I hope you'll still enjoy this clip!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
